description:
CellPerformance: Table storing performance metrics of individual cells in a radio access network.

dateTime: Timestamp of the performance measurement.
Area_Name: Geographic area where the cell is located.
CellId: Unique identifier for the cell.
Id2:  Alternative/redundant cell identifier.
Id3: Another alternative/redundant cell identifier, potentially indicating a specific sector or equipment.
Id4:  Likely an additional identifier, requires further investigation to understand its purpose.
vsDataType: Data type indicator specifying cell performance data.
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the Ericsson-specific data format.
CellPerformance.zzzTemporary1-8:  Placeholder columns containing apparently default values; their meaning is undefined.
CellPerformance.cellPerformanceId: Unique identifier for the specific performance record.
